headline: McDonald's vs. Darden: How to play the restaurant space
summary: On this segment of Good Buy or Goodbye, Hennessy Funds sustainable ETF manager, Bill Davis, takes a closer look at two restaurant stocks: McDonald's (MCD) and Darden Restaurants (DRI). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination.

headline: Survey shows 1/3 of GLP-1 users are lower-income
summary: Investing.com -- A new BTIG survey of more than 1,000 GLP-1 users in the United States found that roughly one-third fall into the lower-income bracket, defined as earning less than $45,000 per year.

headline: Chart (GTLS): 3 Reasons We Love This Stock
summary: Since September 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 105%. But one standout stock has doubled the market - over the past five years, Chart has surged 206% to $199.80 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 22.6% in the last six months thanks to its solid quarterly results, beating the S&P by 7.1%.
